  "problemTitle": "우주왕자 사교파티",
  "bojProblemId": "30390",
  "infoHtml": "<thead><tr><th style=\"width:16%;\">시간 제한</th><th style=\"width:16%;\">메모리 제한</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">제출</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">정답</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">맞힌 사람</th><th style=\"width:17%;\">정답 비율</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1 초 </td><td>1024 MB</td><td>466</td><td>164</td><td>135</td><td>38.136%</td></tr></tbody>",
  "bodyHtml": "\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"description\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>문제</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_description\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t<p>우주왕자 <span style=\"background-color:#000;background-image:linear-gradient(163deg,#000 0%,#ccc 50%,#000 100%);background-size:100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;-moz-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;-moz-text-fill-color:transparent;\"><em><b>VITAS</b></em></span>는 지구인들과 친해지기 위해 사교파티를 열었다. <span style=\"background-color:#000;background-image:linear-gradient(163deg,#000 0%,#ccc 50%,#000 100%);background-size:100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;-moz-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;-moz-text-fill-color:transparent;\"><em><b>VITAS</b></em></span>는 포도주 $A$병과 빵 $B$개를 가지고 있고, 포도주 한 병을 빵 한 개로 바꾸거나 빵 한 개를 포도주 한 병으로 바꾸는 마법을 최대 $K$번 부릴 수 있다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#000;background-image:linear-gradient(163deg,#000 0%,#ccc 50%,#000 100%);background-size:100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;-moz-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;-moz-text-fill-color:transparent;\"><em><b>VITAS</b></em></span>는 초대한 모든 지구인에게 각각 동일한 수의 포도주와 빵을 나눠 줄 것이다. 한 종류를 아무에게도 나눠 주지 않는 것도 가능하다. 단, 포도주와 빵을 나눠주고 난 뒤 남은 것이 있으면 안 된다.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#000;background-image:linear-gradient(163deg,#000 0%,#ccc 50%,#000 100%);background-size:100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;-moz-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;-moz-text-fill-color:transparent;\"><em><b>VITAS</b></em></span>가 위 조건을 만족시키면서 초대할 수 있는 지구인의 수의 최댓값을 구하여라.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"input\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>입력</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_input\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>첫째 줄에 정수 $A$, $B$, $K$가 공백을 사이에 두고 주어진다. $(1 \\le A, B, K \\le 10^{10})$</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"output\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>출력</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_output\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"background-color:#000;background-image:linear-gradient(163deg,#000 0%,#ccc 50%,#000 100%);background-size:100%;-webkit-background-clip:text;-moz-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;-moz-text-fill-color:transparent;\"><em><b>VITAS</b></em></span>가 조건을 만족시키면서 초대할 수 있는 지구인의 수의 최댓값을 출력한다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t<section id=\"limit\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t<h2>제한</h2>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_limit\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 1\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-1\">3 9 1\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 1\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-1\">4\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sample_explain_1\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_sample_explain_1\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>빵 $1$개를 포도주 $1$병으로 바꾸면, $4$명의 지구인에게 각각 포도주 $1$병과&nbsp;빵 $2$개씩을&nbsp;나눠줄 수 있게 된다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 2\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-2\">5 10 3\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput2\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 2\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-2\">5\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sample_explain_2\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_sample_explain_2\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>마법을 사용하지 않는 것이 최적인 경우도 있다.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleinput3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 입력 3\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-input-3\">7 8 7\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sampleoutput3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>예제 출력 3\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre class=\"sampledata\" id=\"sample-output-3\">15\n</pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id=\"sample_explain_3\" class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_sample_explain_3\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>가진 포도주를 모두 빵으로 바꾸면, $15$명의 지구인에게 빵을 $1$개씩 나눠줄 수 있다. 모든 지구인이&nbsp;포도주를 받지 못하는 경우도, 공평하게 포도주가 분배되었고&nbsp;남는 포도주가 없으므로 문제의 조건에 부합함에 유의하라.</p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n\t\t\t\t<section id=\"hint\"  class=\"problem-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headline\">\n\t\t\t\t<h2>힌트</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"problem_hint\" class=\"problem-text\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><iframe allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XyJfprp3r3o\" width=\"560\"></iframe></p>\r\n\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12\"><section id=\"source\"><div class=\"headline\"><h2>출처</h2></div><p>Contest&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;BOJ User Contest&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;월간 향유회&nbsp;&gt;&nbsp;월간 향유회 2023. 10.&nbsp;B번</p><ul><li>문제를 만든 사람:&nbsp;pjshwa</li><li>문제를 검수한 사람:&nbsp;bnb2011, chogahui05, heeda0528, kiwiyou, rustiebeats, snrnsidy, utilforever</li></ul></section></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t"
